lead_paragraph: Dutch teenager Max Verstappen has won Formula One's Driver of the Day award for the third time in nine races after finishing second for Red Bull in Austria on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Verstappen Wins F1 Driver Award for Third Time
headline.main: Verstappen Wins F1 Driver Award for Third Time
